text: Eighteen Years Old (Osmnáctiletá) is a 1939 Czechoslovak drama film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Hana Vítová, Bolek Prchal, and Ladislav Boháč. ==References== ==External links== *Eighteen Years Old (Osmnáctiletá) at the Internet Movie Database Category:1939 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak drama films Category:1939 drama films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black- and-white films
